          <a href="/book/show/12389745-the-night-before-christmas-and-other-popular-stories-for-children"><img id="more_book_12389745" alt="The Night Before Christmas and Other Popular Stories For Children" title="The Night Before Christmas and Other Popular Stories For Children" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1363448793l/12389745._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
